Well it seems the universe had other plans for me over the past few months! 😫😭😩…. A burst Flexi pipe completely flooded my bathroom, wardrobe, bedroom, office and downstairs lounge room all in just a few hours! 

This was my first house emergency. 🚨 and all things considered, I handled it all rather well. I was lucky to have my whole fam rush over to help me pull up the carpet and dry it out as much as we could. 

Fun note: the people who installed the previous carpet (29 years ago) left a few of their old cigarette butts under it. (See last photo) 🤢🤮 

This is a reminder to all who don’t have insurance to GO GET IT!! …. I had building but not contents and I regret it…. A LOT!!! 😮‍💨🥴😭😭😭
